: It is difficult to translate, and also largely irrelevant to the article.  Given that we also don't have articles about most of the names listed, and likely won't (since many of these likely fail notability requirements for English-language readers), I don't expect that this will be added to the article any time soon.  ‑‑&nbsp;[[User:Eirikr|Eiríkr&nbsp;Útlendi]]&nbsp;│<sup>''[[User talk:Eirikr|Tala&nbsp;við&nbsp;mig]]''</sup> 22:40, 20 July 2022 (UTC)
